</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api_1ga1ba636c0efb7a91630ed9743e6fd4d6c" kindref="member">mgmt_cb_return</ref> either <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api_1gga1ba636c0efb7a91630ed9743e6fd4d6cac9a6240975af04d413048d762ca1b0da" kindref="member">MGMT_CB_OK</ref> if all handlers returned it, or <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api_1gga1ba636c0efb7a91630ed9743e6fd4d6ca6ca7c4ba7dc1c300489da4a935b7d990" kindref="member">MGMT_CB_ERROR_RC</ref> if the first failed handler returned an SMP error (in which case <computeroutput>err_rc</computeroutput> will be updated with the SMP error) or <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api_1gga1ba636c0efb7a91630ed9743e6fd4d6cad88f720a1d62658c346e8bebfb81d66d" kindref="member">MGMT_CB_ERROR_ERR</ref> if the first failed handler returned a ret group and error (in which case <computeroutput>err_group</computeroutput> will be updated with the failed group ID and <computeroutput>err_rc</computeroutput> will be updated with the group-specific error code). </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
